-09-24T01:50:25.000Z","msg":"仆街我都以為係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:58:32.000Z","msg":"你有無睇晒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:04:21.000Z","msg":"梳 未訓醒 自吞一打膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地fact check能力真係要學下<br />\n<br />\n認真post冇人理 樓主唔打算推下？"},{"pid":"844c6425f1ee077bf627d7cd5295c18344403d4e","tid":1590752,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1c65a2772d6ffe8d139f951b5886d7693e91d89","tid":1590752,"uid":169413,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T01:50:25.000Z","msg":"仆街我都以為係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:05:44.000Z","msg":"這篇演示提供了一些驗證圖像的技術，希望對您有所幫助。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">通過驗證，您基本上可以證明它是真實的，您所看到的事確實發生了，並且知道了它的拍攝位置和大致時間，有足夠的詳細信息以使其有用。</span><br />\n<br />\n社交媒體信息驗證非常重要 &mdash;&mdash;在2017年，國際刑事法院僅根據社交媒體信息為證據發布了第一份逮捕令；利比亞指揮官韋法裡（Werfalli）被控犯有戰爭罪的全部證據&mdash; &mdash;七個視頻&mdash;&mdash;都是在社交網絡上找到的。<br />\n<br />\n社交媒體開源信息是潛在的證據金礦；但前提是，必須經過科學的驗證。<br />\n<br />\n希望本演示能幫助中國民間的獨立調查人員掌握挖掘證據的方法：<br />\n請記得《什麼才能算是證據、以及如何拿到證據》<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kZ0mLV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kZ0mLV&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obvMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=86c458d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kZ0mLV</a> ，這篇詳細介紹非常重要。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中文原文：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2m5s4Ha\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2m5s4Ha&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obvMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=be6eb4b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2m5s4Ha</a><br />\n<br />\nTWITTER英文原文：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Nrg8000/status/1175353408749891584?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/